query:
INSERT INTO server (
        user_id,
        project_id,
        region,
        zone,
        server,
        os,
        disk_type,
        created_at,
        updated_at,
        srv_ip,
        ssh_user,
        ssh_port
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, NOW() at time zone 'utc',NOW() at time zone 'utc', $8, $9, $10)
        RETURNING id;
